          { "q": "What is the catalog?", "a": "A public list of active giveaways from all creators. Participants can discover new giveaways without searching channels." },
          { "q": "How do I get into the catalog?", "a": "When creating a giveaway, enable 'Add to Catalog'. For PLUS+ and PRO+ subscribers, giveaways are added automatically." }
        ]
      },
